                                 README
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The example illustrates the communication between two components, and how TLM
classes can be used to create ports and exports to send data between the two.
ComponentA initiates data transfer by calling the task put (), whose implementa
tion is decided by ComponentB.

      .------------------.                       .------------------.
      |   ComponentA     |Port ----------> Export|    ComponentB    |
      '------------------'                       '------------------'

In the next session, we'll see how ComponentB can request for data from 
ComponentA using get () methods.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

